reviews.text:
Absolutely overpriced and the noddle isn’t spectacular. 
You can get better local noodles anywhere away from star street for half the price.
My to go place. Seriously big bowl of noodles. Enough for two for a normal person. Consistent taste
Worth trying Taiwanese noodles, simple and delicious
Pricy, that’s all
There’s a lamborghini shop near here. So you can find it easily. Little salty for me.
